                                K Alarm v1.0.0
                               ----------------

1. Introduction
---------------
  
  This program is to alarm one time, at regular intervals or weekly.

  This program performs the following features on alarm.
  
    - Showing a message window

    - Playing a sound file
    
    - Executing a program
    
