5. Installation
---------------

  Put kalarm.exe into any directory. If you need translations, copy *.qm in 
translations directory into the directory where kalarm.exe exists or the 
translations directory of the directory where kalarm.exe exists.

6. Usage
--------

6.1 Menu
--------

