6.2.4 Close on title bar
------------------------

  Quit a program unless a tray icon is availble. Otherwise, K Alarm is hidden 
instead of quitting. To quit K Alarm, use [File - Exit] or [Tray icon - Exit].

6.3 Hot keys
------------------

