6.4.2.1 Open K Alarm...
-----------------------

  Show K Alarm.
  
6.4.2.2 Help - About K Alarm...
-------------------------------

  Show informations for K Alarm.
  
6.4.2.3 Help - About Qt...
--------------------------

  Show informations for Qt used by K Alarm.

