10.2 How to Download the sources
--------------------------------

  The following git repository is provided,
  
      git://github.com/komh/kalarm.git
      
  To download the sources, do like below.
    
      git clone git://github.com/komh/kalarm.git
      
  To update,
  
      git pull

10.3 How to compile
-------------------
  
  If you get the sources, then execute qmake.
  
      qmake
      
  After qmake completes, execute make.
  
      make
      
  Then you can get kalarm.exe.

  If you want to use Qt Creator, then execute Qt Creator and open kalarm.pro. 
And build it using Ctrl-B.
  
